snippet.title: Kalyskah - Steam Announcement!
snippet.description:
Hello everyone!
The road so far has been hard, we've been putting our blood and sweat to try and bring you a vampire game that we always wanted to play, and there's still a long way to go. Still, it is with a lot of happiness that we come today to announce that you can finally wishlist our game on Steam!

You can do so by following this link:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1818660/Kalyskah/
